%******************************************************************************
\chapter{Compression}
%******************************************************************************
% libflate

%claude:
[[libflate]] implements the deflate/inflate algorithms
(RFC~1951) used by [[gzip]] and [[gunzip]]. The library
provides a callback-based streaming interface: the caller
supplies read and write functions, and [[deflate]]/[[inflate]]
process data in chunks without loading the entire file into
memory.

